---
title: 系統部署架構
---
flowchart TB
    subgraph Edge["邊緣層"]
        CDN[CDN]
        WAF[WAF 防火牆]
    end
    subgraph App["應用層"]
        LB[負載平衡器]
        API1[API Server 1]
        API2[API Server 2]
        Worker[背景工作排程]
    end
    subgraph Data["資料層"]
        DB[(主資料庫)]
        Replica[(讀取副本)]
        Cache[(Redis 快取)]
        MQ[/訊息佇列/]
    end
    User((使用者)) --> CDN --> WAF --> LB
    LB --> API1
    LB --> API2
    API1 --> Cache
    API2 --> Cache
    API1 --> DB
    API2 --> Replica
    API1 -.-> MQ -.-> Worker
    Worker --> DB
    DB -. 複寫 .-> Replica
